name: compiler_deep_v8_cross_predicate_after_mutated_array_index
section: feature-interactions-v8
args: p:Bool a:Int b:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: A mutable index should drive array-as-function lookup before predicate checking.
law: (Int? (with [xs [{a} {b}] i 0] (do (when {p} (set! i 1)) (xs i))))
